id: pm-8og4
title: "CodeQL alert 27: js/polynomial-redos in sdk/test/linked-command-detection.ts trailing-dash prefix trim"
description: "GitHub code scanning (CodeQL) alert #27 (created 2026-07-16, open): extractReferencedPmItemIdsFromCommand normalizes the workspace id prefix with idPrefix.trim().toLowerCase().replace(/-+$/, \"\") at src/sdk/test/linked-command-detection.ts:318. The /-+$/ pattern backtracks polynomially on adversarial prefixes consisting of long dash runs that fail to anchor at end-of-string. The prefix flows from workspace settings (id_prefix), so a hostile tracker config or crafted settings file can degrade linked-test governance scans. Duplicate check: Semgrep items (pm-t8e9 lineage) cover non-literal RegExp construction in the old src/cli/commands paths, a different rule and site; no existing item tracks CodeQL alert 27."
