acceptance_criteria: "The trailing-dash trim runs in linear time (index scan or equivalent, no ambiguous quantifier before an end anchor); CodeQL alert 27 closes on the default branch after merge; a regression test exercises a pathological dash-run prefix and asserts fast, correct normalization; behavior for normal prefixes is unchanged"
